<TITLE> Upazila chairman to get budget allocation: local govt minister </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Chittagong, Dec 12 (bdnews24.com)  Upazila chairmen will get a separate allocation in the national budget from next year, local government minister Syed Ashraful Islam said on Saturday. He said the government will also issue a circular shortly settling the responsibilities of upazila chairmen and upazila nirbahi officers. The minister was sharing opinions with upazila chairmen at the Chittagong Circuit House on Saturday. In another meeting at the Circuit House with high officials of various government agencies in Chittagong, Ashraf warned that action will be taken against any tender-mongers overlooking any partisanship with any political party. Chittagong city corporation mayor ABM Mohiuddin Chowdhury, divisional commissioner ANM Siddique and Chittagong Metropolitan Police commissioner Md Maniruzzaman were present among others in both the meetings. bdn
